<style>
    *,
    ::before,
    ::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
</style>

<main style="width: 21cm; min-height: 29.7cm; margin: 2rem; font-family: Heebo, sans-serif;">
    <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">{{ invoice.type }}</h1>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem; color: gray">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.reference }}</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Le {{ invoice.date }}</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">A {{ invoice.time }}</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">{{ invoice.from }}</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px;">{{ invoice.to }}</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <table style="border-collapse: collapse">
            <tbody>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Nom</th>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Description</th>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Quantite</th>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Prix unitaire</th>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Reduction</th>
                        <th style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: start">Prix total</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.logement.name }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.logement.description }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">1</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.logement.price }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.logement.discount }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.logement.total }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.taxes.adults.name }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adults.description }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adults.quantity }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adults.price }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">/</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adults.total }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.taxes.children.name }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.children.description }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.children.quantity }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.children.price }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">/</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.children.total }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.taxes.adultsPool.name }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adultsPool.description }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adultsPool.quantity }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adultsPool.price }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">/</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.adultsPool.total }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.taxes.childrenPool.name }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.childrenPool.description }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.childrenPool.quantity }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.childrenPool.price }}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">/</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0.5rem;">{{ invoice.taxes.childrenPool.total }}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Total</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1.2rem; color: gray">Total : <span style="font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.total.pretax }}</span></p>
        {% if invoice.total.highseasontax %}
            <p style="margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1.2rem; color: gray">Taxe haute saison : <span style="font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.total.highseasontax }}</span></p>
        {% endif %}
        <p style="margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 1.5rem">Total a payer : <span style="font-weight: bold">{{ invoice.total.total }}</span></p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p style="color: gray">Merci de faire confiance a l'Espadrille Volante, a bient√¥t dans notre camping !</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p style="color: #B0413E">Nous vous conseillons d'enregistrer cette facture sous peine de ne plus la retrouver par la suite. Cependant, si vous possedez un compte sur L'Espadrille Volante, vous pourrez retrouver toutes vos reservations et factures dans votre espace personnel.</p>
    </div>
</main>